Mesh

Directories:
	Mesh	- basic mesh code
	Operators - operators for modifying the mesh
	UserData  - tagging the mesh with basic user data geometry
	U2	  - a varient of UserData

You'll find documentation in the Doc directory.

Simple programs live in the TestPrograms directory.  This
includes io.c, icosahedron.c, path.c, and t.c.

Programs of interest in the the Apps directory include:

    4Color	- a program to 4 color a triangular mesh
    FlipMesh	- a program to reverse the orientation of a mesh
    Smooth	- a program to "smooth" a mesh.
    Stellate	- a program to stellate a mesh.
    Normal	- Several normal tagging programs 

